        - fields (username, email, password) must be clear;

Steps To Reproduce
1) enter cred ('wnqcsgwuourgowyobu') in username field
2) enter cred ('wnqcsgwuourgowyobu@tmmbt.com') in password field
3) Click 'Sign In' button

    Expected Result:
